c57567e93fa4914365fffaf15b1a6937f28b5ee1.query:
INSERT INTO plugins (
                plugin_id,
                plugin_type,
                display_name,
                tenant_id,
                artifact_s3_key
            )
            VALUES ($1::uuid, $2, $3, $4::uuid, $5)
            ON CONFLICT DO NOTHING;

d31a831ff688cfe70f5ba3fc527acac049d9312d.query:
SELECT
            plugin_id,
            tenant_id,
            display_name,
            plugin_type,
            artifact_s3_key
            FROM plugins
            WHERE plugin_id = $1
